## Drag Handle Position

**Standard:** Upper-right corner

```tsx
// In SortableWidget or drag handle component
<div className="absolute top-2 right-2 cursor-grab">  {/* ✅ Upper-right */}
  <svg>...</svg>  {/* Drag handle icon */}
</div>

// ❌ Incorrect - Upper-left (overlaps icon/title)
<div className="absolute top-2 left-2">
```

**Rationale:** Upper-left position overlaps widget icon/title (hard to see). Upper-right is clear and accessible.

