## Typography

### Widget Title

```tsx
<h3 className="text-sm font-semibold text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary mb-2">
  Widget Title (3)  {/* Count badge optional */}
</h3>
```

**Required Classes:**
- `text-sm` - 14px font size
- `font-semibold` - 600 font weight
- `text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary` - Semantic text color
- `mb-2` - 8px bottom margin (before content)

---

### List Item Text

```tsx
<li className="text-sm text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary">
  List item content
</li>
```

**Required Classes:**
- `text-sm` - 14px font size (matches title)
- `text-text-light-primary dark:text-text-dark-primary` - Semantic text color

---

### Secondary Text (Metadata)

```tsx
<p className="text-xs text-text-light-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary">
  Due tomorrow · High priority
</p>
```

**Required Classes:**
- `text-xs` - 12px font size (smaller than primary)
- `text-text-light-secondary dark:text-text-dark-secondary` - Muted text color

