## Migration Checklist

When updating existing widgets to meet standards:

1. **Before/After Screenshot**
   - Take screenshot before changes
   - Take screenshot after changes
   - Compare to ensure no regressions

2. **Spacing Audit**
   - [ ] Change widget padding to `p-4`
   - [ ] Change content spacing to `space-y-4`
   - [ ] Change list spacing to `space-y-3`
   - [ ] Remove extra bottom spacing

3. **Button Standardization**
   - [ ] Change button to `w-full px-4 py-2`
   - [ ] Verify button height is 40px
   - [ ] Update accent color if needed

4. **Testing**
   - [ ] Test in light mode
   - [ ] Test in dark mode
   - [ ] Test on mobile/tablet/desktop
   - [ ] Compare with other widgets (should match)

5. **Documentation**
   - [ ] Update component comments if needed
   - [ ] Add to feature map if new widget type

